Aditi Arora (Saloni – Atma’s Younger Daughter). Chandan Anand (Kailash – Saloni’s Husband). Anil Charanjeett (Jhandu Singh). Rajiv Nema (Vijay – Atma’s Co-passenger). Sharad Vyas (Tiwari – Atmaram’s Friend). Shubham Tiwari (Atmaram Dubey – Younger). Ida Ali (Sarla Dubey – Younger). Preety Ali (Sarla Dubey). Dimpy Mishra (Salon Owner). R. Krishnan Singh (Barber #1). Mukesh Pachode (Barber #2 (as Mukesh Pachede)). Razia Khanam (Phoolwanti (as Razia Khan)). Harsh Daund (Girish Agarwal). Devendra Bisht (Rakesh – Santulan’s Friend). Saaket Chouhan (Guddu – Santulan’s Friend). Aamir Khan (Prajapatee – Santulan’s Friend). Ahmad Raza Khan (Salim Bandwala). Uday Chandra (Pehalwan). Garima Vikrant Singh (Jugnu’s Wife (as Garima Vikram Singh)). Nayan Raghuvanshi (Santulan’s Wife). Jeniffer Piccinato (Thai Girl on Massage Card). Kailash Chauhan (Sadhu #1). Monty Baba (Sadhu #2). Rajesh Junwal (Paanwala). Kamal Jain (Pehalwan’s Son). Mayank Mathur (Pehelwan’s Son). Aashriya Mishra (Honey – Saloni’s Daughter). Pratyaksh Panwar (Chikki – Mukesh’s Son). Arit Panwar (Kid Gonu – Mukesh’s Son). Pratyaksh Sharma (Toddler Gonu – Mukesh’s Son). Vaishnavi Jha (Santulan’s Daughter). Swastika Chakraborty (Neighbour Lady). Dhruv Acharya (Chintan). Chhaya Mundra (Chintan’s Mom). Balendar Singh (Chintan’s Dad (as Balendra Singh)). Pradeep Nema (Atma’s Friend in Garden). Siddhant Mishra (TV Anchor). Shobha Chatterjee (Hiramani – Tiwari’s Wife). Savi Bhandari (Santulan’s Wife’s Friend). Anil Sharma (Baapuji). Kusum Shastri (Pehalwan’s Wife #1). Divya Singh (Pehalwan’s Wife #2). Nan Seing Lein Kham (Escort in Red Dress). Angel Shetty (Sona)

Language Hindi

Producers Murshid Akhtar . Imtiaz Ali . Abhishek Gupta . Karan Kasle . Nidhi Sethia.

Production Reliance Entertainment. T-Series. Window Seat Films.
